vide a new perspective for a better understanding of the dynamical\nstructure of theories of interacting spin-two fields, which does not require\nthe constraints to be catalogued as first- and second-class ones as in the case\nof Dirac's standard method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Apr 2020 19:48:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2021 22:50:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-25"}
