andom guessing. This result demonstrates how\ncontextual information can aid transient classifications at the time of first\ndetection. In the current era of spectroscopically-starved time-domain\nastronomy, prompt automated classification is paramount.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 May 2020 00:37:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-21"}
